span.p: The College Board announced Wednesday, April 15, that it has canceled the administration of June 6 SAT and SAT Subject Tests. Click for more information.
Governor Andrew Cuomo has extended NYS on PAUSE through May 15, 2020, meaning all schools will be closed through May 15. Click for more information.
Gov. Andrew Cuomo has issued an Executive Order that postpones all school budget votes and Board of Education elections until at least June 1. Click for more information.
